OL,6,FChildren as young as 13 have been
OL,7,Fhospitalised after using vapes spiked
OL,8,Fwith dangerous drugs like spice and
OL,9,Ffentanyl.
OL,11,FITV News analysis of official police
OL,12,Fdata reveals vape spiking is a new
OL,13,Femerging threat.
OL,15,FOne teenage girl from Teesside
OL,16,Fcollapsed at school after trying a
OL,17,Freusable vape containing the zombie
OL,18,Fdrug spice while she was in a
OL,19,Fclassroom.
