OL,6,F"It was scary," she said. "The teacher
OL,7,Fwas talking to me but I was throwing
OL,8,Fup and passing out."
OL,10,F'Polly', 13, whose identity we are
OL,11,Fprotecting due to her young age, told
OL,12,FITV News she had been left traumatised
OL,13,Fby the "near death" experience in
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,F"When I was in the ambulance, the lady
OL,17,Fsaid to me, 'Don't close your eyes in
OL,18,Fcase you don't wake back up'. I kept
OL,19,Flooking at her, but everything kept
OL,20,Fgoing weird."
