OL,6,FSpice is a synthetic substance known
OL,7,Fas the zombie drug because in extreme
OL,8,Fcases it can cause breathing
OL,9,Fdifficulties, psychosis and muscle
OL,10,Fspasms. The class B drug is also
OL,11,Fhighly addictive.
OL,13,FThe teenager was rushed to hospital
OL,14,Fwhere doctors later told her mother
OL,15,FDeborah that if her daughter had taken
OL,16,F"one more puff" she could have had a
OL,17,Fheart attack.
